{"tid":1745814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［最後衝刺］民調跌少少就唉聲嘆氣，呢兩日要大建連儂牆","createTime":"2019-11-22T11:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T08:59:29.000Z","uid":55043,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"810512fb03ee9edcea4d6b158155371e34b2c581","tid":1745814,"uid":55043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"學羅范名句<br />\n<br />\n如果真係因為黎明行動，民調點會跌咁少？搞到沉默大多數wo?<br />\n<br />\n與其響度指責邊個搞輸，不如行動去贏<br />\n<br />\n民意最大武器就係幅牆，近排幅牆被清既情況同所謂民意逆轉既情況更為吻合<br />\n<br />\n冇左牆既資訊，所謂游離人士就只係睇到CCTVB，所以呢兩日請砌牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你話砌牆都驚，咁唔好話自己抗爭緊，仲話要還拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bf149a4a85b697f6a28266955906dda18abdc3","tid":1745814,"uid":312332,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:54:21.000Z","msg":"仲未明政府咩玩法既人留意<br />\n<br />\n你200萬+1人上街，佢屈9你20萬人<br />\n你5個月黎示威，佢屈你一少撮人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你只能夠講你計唔準，但佢可以話你都唔準，口同鼻拗</span><br />\n但係今次區選當公投，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係實打實既數字</span><br />\n＜就算對方種票，佢都要有身份證，影響既只會係<span style=\"color: red;\">地區議席分布，而唔係黃藍人數</span>＞<br />\n440幾萬選民，唔可能變500萬張選票<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">宜家應該係煲大區選</span><br />\n   投建制派=支持止暴制亂<br />\n   投黃投獨立=沒有暴動，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n結果一出黎<br />\n黃票多過200萬，政府<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以再講一少撮人</span><br />\n藍票低過200萬，<span style=\"color: red;\">輪到我地屈佢一少撮人</span><br />\n<br />\n宜家係要煲大佢<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">   投建制派=支持止暴制亂 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">  投黃投獨立=沒有暴動，只有暴政</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">選舉人數輸左=玻璃球打爛左</span><br />\n打爛左個玻璃球既後果係<br />\n1：運動失敗，逃亡潮開始<br />\n2：勇武轉化革命份子，引發更大暴力<br />\n3：香港政府管治失敗<br />\n<br />\n如果無更大暴力事件，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁你都輸得甘心命抵啦，仲唔快手著草</span><br />\n輸唔起就係你起革命，唔係逃避現實<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n咪發傻阻礙區選，比個位政府入<br />\n話你地一少撮人唔願意面對現實<br />\n<br />\n如果區選人頭黃多過藍，你仲可以反口話政府唔願面對現實，實實在在既數字啊<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n目標唔係含投<br />\n係要打倒建制派，無黃議員都要推假獨立<br />\n刷低對方明面上議席，清除舊有垃圾<br />\n新垃圾到時先諗計清，推到班假獨立起碼對方可以做25仔/牆頭草，唔係宜家一面倒垃圾建制派<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔覺得係公投，對家都會煲大佢變公投<br />\n先發制人<br />\n咁樣先可以動員更多港豬<br />\n<br />\n我幾個上年紀既同事仲發傻諗住唔投票<br />\n要同佢講對家會當今次係公投，先on99夢醒<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n無證無據話對方做假，大陸吹一堆假消息已經玩爛個真相<br />\n<br />\n中共外國超多打手玩假英文消息<br />\n<br />\n你要證明一件事有問題，就係要你舉出證據<br />\n否則只會當你自欺欺人<br />\n雖然信你既人會好多，但係外國佬無辦法直接插手，無證據點放上枱啊<br />\n<br />\n你今次煲大佢，<br />\n一係對方唔做手腳<br />\n黃票真係多，我地贏<br />\n<br />\n一係對方做手腳<br />\n我地/外國捉到對方做手腳，我地都贏<br />\n<br />\n捉唔到對方做手腳，就到時做文宣講選舉有問題啦<br />\n結果都係返到去，無證據，對方信定唔信<br />\n<br />\n點玩都咁被動，點解唔認真d投票"},{"pid":"94de5721ce2d153aade36ed205dc343335e8d49d","tid":1745814,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5cf778e0b140cc0ddbc7d0b08a99d8ed53efd1","tid":1745814,"uid":5373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"今日隧道有camp狗 要小心 不宜久留"},{"pid":"fd62102a0bebb8e2e332ec8ffe2e212678f733c2","tid":1745814,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:05:33.000Z","msg":"選完先"},{"pid":"1f108d59f7359aa486223a2d75ea49894e27c5fb","tid":1745814,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先75%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=468cb9dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=08986c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"739af2cb2629e359a975953646a9e0754848ab7e","tid":1745814,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=c7991ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=bf90348d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=a05e9062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=a39bb56c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc24ec731302b084346020e0204d2a93f70db35e","tid":1745814,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:09:44.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e14fc91de461e2cb33f0dc8d5bb6cfcf6ae0f2a2","tid":1745814,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"810512fb03ee9edcea4d6b158155371e34b2c581","tid":1745814,"uid":5504